        "Description": "Agent 47,\rWelcome to f NYC where dreams are crushed and egos soar. Three individuals seek for some financial adjustments. Two trust the high\rground—but danger often rises from deep below. The third? Let&apos;s just say his last transaction will be injected. When it&apos;s done, don&apos;t loiter—there&apos;s an escape out of this, but it&apos;s reserved for those climbing the corporate ladder of the concrete jail. Be careful. Time to cash out, 47.\rCheers,\rBurgers\rJoin us at https://discord.gg/u25Gpyq6\rby: notbobsburgers",
